picas (<colour id="7" />♠<colour id="65535" />) o tréboles (<colour id="7" />♣<colour id="65535" />)?</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="6" />Corazones (♥)<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="6" />Diamantes (♦)<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="7" />Picas (♠)<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_d" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="7" />Tréboles (♣)<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Pues sí!<delay20 /> ¡Eran <tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />!
<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Es como <10_5 />super<endTag a="10" b="5" />impresionante que
hayas acertado.</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Eran <tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /> ¡Qué lástima que hayas fallado!</message>
